title: Penny Skateboards- Holiday Series
description:
Check out the Holiday Series from Penny Skateboards, featuring a number of funky designs, including Hawaiian, Aztec, Polka and Resin. This range introduces a number of new patterns, inspired by current fashion trends.

This video features professional skateboarders in a controlled environment. Always skate within your limits, have fun and get out there! 

Skater: Jackson Pilz
Music By: DJ Slynk
